      "para_id": "Q001449.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Ur-gigira , military governor of Dumuzid , child of Ur-niĝin , the powerful man , king of Unug , and Ama-lagar , his mother , built for Ninšešeĝara , his lady , the E-šešeĝara , her beloved temple , in Patibira ."
    }
  ],
